The paper deals with compressive sensing, which is a subfield of information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SP). The focus is on multi-channel data, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses applications in computer vision (cs.CV).
